7.9.11

(a)

n = 100
set.seed(10)
X1 = rnorm(n)
X2 = rnorm(n)
Y = rnorm(n)

(b)

beta1 = 0.4

(c)

a = Y-beta1*X1
beta2=lm(a~X2)$coef[2]

(d)

a = Y - beta2*X2
beta1=lm(a~X1)$coef[2]

(e)

b0 = 1
e = 0.1
Y = X1*beta1+X2*beta2+b0+e

res=matrix(NA,3,1000,dimnames=list(c("C0","C1","C2"),paste(1:1000)))

for(i in seq(1000)){
  a = Y-beta1*X1
  b2=lm(a~X2)$coef[2]
  a = Y - beta2*X2
  b1=lm(a~X1)$coef[2]
  res["C0",i]=b0
  res["C1",i]=b1
  res["C2",i]=b2
}

res[,c(1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9,1000), drop=F]
